## Section B: Community Sentiment — Postmill Thread Analysis

The following threads were harvested from [Postmill](http://localhost:9999) across four sub-forums: `/f/electricvehicles`, `/f/teslamotors`, `/f/cars`, and `/f/BuyItForLife`. Each entry includes the thread URL, forum, score, comment count, a summary of the top-voted take, and a classification.

### B.1 /f/electricvehicles

| # | Thread URL | Score | Comments | Top-Voted Summary | Classification |
|---|-----------|-------|----------|-------------------|---------------|
| 1 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/1-best-ev-road-trip-accessories](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/1-best-ev-road-trip-accessories) | 342 | 89 | "Must-have accessories are a Level 2 portable charger, a tire inflator, and a CCS adapter for non-Tesla chargers — skip the overpriced brand-name cables." | purchase_advice |
