| 3 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/3-dash-cam-importance](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/3-dash-cam-importance) | 178 | 54 | "A dash cam is essential for EV road trips to document charging station incidents and parking lot damage — VIOFO and Garmin are top brands." | praise |
| 4 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/4-tire-inflator-essential](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/4-tire-inflator-essential) | 156 | 43 | "EVs are heavier than gas cars, so tire pressure changes more with temperature — a good inflator like the AstroAI saved my trip twice." | praise |
| 5 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/5-range-anxiety-solutions](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/5-range-anxiety-solutions) | 298 | 112 | "Plan your routes with A Better Routeplanner, keep a 12V jump starter just in case, and always carry a CCS adapter — that kills range anxiety." | technical_question |
| 6 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/6-sunshade-recommendations](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/6-sunshade-recommendations) | 134 | 38 | "EVs with glass roofs bake in the sun — a WeatherTech custom sunshade for Tesla Model 3/Y is worth every penny." | praise |
| 7 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/7-jump-starter-ev-compatibility](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/7-jump-starter-ev-compatibility) | 201 | 76 | "Make sure the jump starter is lithium-ion and has reverse polarity protection — NOCO Boost Plus is the gold standard for EVs." | technical_question |
| 8 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/8-cable-management-tips](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/8-cable-management-tips) | 89 | 31 | "A simple cable organizer pouch and magnetic cable ties keep the frunk tidy — Baseus and Anker make decent budget options." | purchase_advice |
| 9 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/9-portable-battery-solutions](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/9-portable-battery-solutions) | 234 | 78 | "The Jackery Explorer 240 is great for powering devices on long road trips, but the ECOFLOW RIVER 2 charges faster and is more compact." | comparison |
| 10 | [http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/10-best-ev-road-trip-inflators](http://localhost:9999/f/electricvehicles/10-best-ev-road-trip-inflators) | 167 | 52 | "The Fanttik X8 Pro is the best cordless inflator for EVs — it's compact, accurate, and can top off all four tires on a single charge." | comparison |

